'''傑克·哈珀'''（{{lang-en|'''Jack Harper'''}}；{{bd|1996年|2月28日}}）是一位[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]足球運動員。在場上的位置是前鋒。現時被[[西甲|西甲]]球隊[[赫塔費足球俱樂部|基達菲]]外借至[[西班牙皇家足協甲組聯賽|西班牙皇家足協甲組聯賽]]球隊[[桑坦德競賽|桑坦德競賽]]，曾效力[[布萊頓足球俱樂部|布萊頓]]<ref >{{citenews |language =en |url =http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/33636770 |title =Real Madrid's Jack Harper joins Brighton & Hove Albion |work =''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date =2015-07-23 |accessdate =2015-10-25 |archive-date =2015-09-24 |archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150924225132/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/33636770 |dead-url =no }}</ref>。他出生在[[西班牙|西班牙]]<ref name = "Madrid">{{cite web|url=http://www.realmadrid.com/en/football/academy/under-19/jack-harper|title=Profile|accessdate=8 November 2013|publisher=Real Madrid C.F.|archive-date=2018-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180819083050/https://www.realmadrid.com/en/football/academy/under-19/jack-harper|dead-url=no}}</ref>，父母都是蘇格蘭人<ref name = "WSC">{{cite web|url=http://www.wsc.co.uk/wsc-daily/1160-march-2013/9614-playing-abroad-is-a-good-option-for-britain-s-prospects|title=Playing abroad can work for Britain's prospects|date=30 March 2013|accessdate=6 April 2013|author=Scott Johnson|publisher=When Saturday Comes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305073447/http://www.wsc.co.uk/wsc-daily/1160-march-2013/9614-playing-abroad-is-a-good-option-for-britain-s-prospects|archive-date=2016-03-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。他的兄弟瑞安·哈珀和麥克·哈珀也是足球運動員。

